<text id="02-output-contract" title="pytest Async Testing — Output Contract" version="1.0.0" est_tokens="800" depth="essential">
  <summary>Output schema for the subagent applying python-pytest-async. Encodes required boolean checks against the artefact under review.</summary>

  <section title="Schema (JSON Schema fragment)">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "$schema": "https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema",
  "type": "object",
  "required": ['asyncio_mode_auto', 'uses_pytest_asyncio_fixture', 'asyncmock_for_async', 'asgitransport_for_fastapi'],
  "properties": {
    "asyncio_mode_auto": { "type": "boolean" },
    "uses_pytest_asyncio_fixture": { "type": "boolean" },
    "asyncmock_for_async": { "type": "boolean" },
    "asgitransport_for_fastapi": { "type": "boolean" }
  },
  "additionalProperties": false
}
]]></code>
  </section>

  <section title="Required fields">
    <list>
      <item>asyncio_mode_auto</item>
      <item>uses_pytest_asyncio_fixture</item>
      <item>asyncmock_for_async</item>
      <item>asgitransport_for_fastapi</item>
    </list>
  </section>

  <section title="Valid example">
    <example type="good">
      <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "asyncio_mode_auto": true,
  "uses_pytest_asyncio_fixture": true,
  "asyncmock_for_async": true,
  "asgitransport_for_fastapi": true
}
]]></code>
      <note>All gates green; methodology applied.</note>
    </example>
  </section>

  <section title="Invalid example">
    <example type="bad">
      <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "asyncio_mode_auto": false,
  "uses_pytest_asyncio_fixture": false,
  "asyncmock_for_async": false,
  "asgitransport_for_fastapi": false
}
]]></code>
      <note>All gates red; methodology not applied — fix the violations before claiming completion.</note>
    </example>
  </section>

  <section title="Self-check checklist">
    <list>
      <item>Every required field is present and boolean true.</item>
      <item>Artefact references the rule id from 01-core-rules.xml (e.g., r1-asyncio-mode-auto).</item>
      <item>No extra properties outside the schema.</item>
    </list>
  </section>
</text>
